# LLM-reported issues — commit README + TEMPLATE, keep user-specific
# pending/submitted/dismissed reports local. Once filed to GitHub, the
# GitHub issue is the canonical record; the local file is a transient
# working copy, not part of the project history.
reports/llm-issues/pending/
reports/llm-issues/submitted/
reports/llm-issues/dismissed/

